description: Retrieves the details for the profile specified by the profile ID. A profile is the mechanism used to create the concept of a private network.

parameters.name: profileId
parameters.description: Specifies the unique, system-generated identifier for the profile.

nested_items.name: profileId
nested_items.description: Returns the unique, system-generated identifier for the profile.

nested_items.name: profileArn
nested_items.description: Returns an Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for a specific Amazon Web Services resource, such as a capability, partnership, profile, or transformer.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: Returns the name of the profile, used to identify it.

nested_items.name: email
nested_items.description: Returns the email address associated with this customer profile.

nested_items.name: phone
nested_items.description: Returns the phone number associated with the profile.

nested_items.name: businessName
nested_items.description: Returns the name for the business associated with this profile.

nested_items.name: logging
nested_items.description: Returns whether or not logging is enabled for this profile.

nested_items.name: logGroupName
nested_items.description: Returns the name of the logging group.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: Returns a timestamp for creation date and time of the transformer.

nested_items.name: modifiedAt
nested_items.description: Returns a timestamp for last time the profile was modified.
